data.description:
Historic charm meets modern convenience in this stunning remodeled 1908 Victorian, just steps to Highlands Square.
This home is thoughtfully renovated with a designer’s eye for detail, including: custom gourmet kitchen, beautiful master suite, open floor plan, new hardwoods, fully finished basement, and high-end finishes and fixtures. Enjoy turn-of-the-century charm with
elegant original features including a tile fireplace, oak mantle and brass insert, refinished woodwork, and built-in hutch. High-tech conveniences including app controlled Nest thermostats, low voltage AV wiring and in-wall speakers are just a few of the modern touches added. Rest easy with the peace of mind of brand new items including: two new high-efficient HVAC systems, roof, plumbing, electrical, paint and landscaping.

Perfectly located just steps to Highlands Square in the coveted Alan Ghost Historic District.
One year builder warranty included.
